strings: <voice_0x01000ECF><se_low>*: If it weren't for Prince Charles, he would be Prince Charles. Wouldn't it be better to do this before you start?

<voice_0x01000ED7><se_low>*: Ok, I hope you enjoyed your hunt. You must...

<voice_0x01000ED6><se_low>*: You must always be on your guard. Remember that the only way to find an Argan Lizard is to hide behind it.
<voice_0x01000EDD><se_high>*: wait a minute Find out more about Old Salamango and start from scratch. what should i do
